metadata.name: Moma Lisa
metadata.description:
Considered an archetypal masterpiece of the blockchain renaissance, JPEG has been described as "the most famous, most visited, most written, most celebrated and most parodied work of art in the NFT world."
The Moma Lisa bears a strong resemblance to numerous NFT Renaissance depictions of the Virgin Mary, which were considered the ideal of womanhood at the time.

My intropritation of a famous painting, drawn according to all the canons of the original. Drawing was performed with the help of hands and a computer mouse.
